Process Management
-------------------
What is a program?
Program is nothing but a File in which we store instructions that can be passed as an input to the operating system asking to execute.
	
	











































	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	

















































	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	













